comments: McCaw (TOR) places a marginal hand to Rozier's (CHA) front during the drive.
Lowry (TOR) makes marginal contact with Monk's (CHA) body during his shooting motion on the play at the basket.
Zeller (CHA) brushes Ibaka's (TOR) head during the rebound and the contact is marginal.
Ibaka (TOR) makes incidental contact with Monk's (CHA) arm after the release on the play at the basket.
Rozier (CHA) makes marginal contact with Ibaka's (TOR) arm and doesn't affect his ability to maintain control of the ball.
Zeller (CHA) makes marginal contact with Ibaka's (TOR) body during his shooting motion on the play at the basket.
Anunoby (TOR) makes contact with Washington (CHA) on the drive that affects his SQBR.
Ibaka (TOR) grabs Biyombo's (CHA) shorts and pull them away from his body during the free throw attempt.
Anunoby (TOR) briefly grasps Biyombo (CHA) before releasing following the pick.
Ibaka (TOR) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Lowry (TOR) makes marginal contact with Bridges (CHA) before gathering the ball during the drive.
Rozier (CHA) and Anunoby (TOR) briefly engage and separate off-ball.
Ibaka (TOR) sets the pick in Washington's (CHA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Washington (CHA) makes marginal contact with Lowry's (TOR) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Ibaka (TOR) holds Washington's (CHA) jersey before the ball is inbounded.
McCaw (TOR) initiates contact with Rozier (CHA) as Rozier screens, but the contact is marginal.
McCaw (TOR) initiates contact with Graham's (CHA) body on the perimeter but the contact is marginal.
Lowry (TOR) legally contests Graham's (CHA) shot attempt at the buzzer.
Zeller (CHA) makes marginal contact with Lowry (TOR) that doesn't affect his SQBR after the pick.
Lowry (TOR) makes marginal contact with Washington (CHA) off ball before cleanly dislodging the ball.
Ibaka (TOR) jumps alongside Graham's (CHA) body and makes marginal contact during his driving shot attempt.
Washington (CHA) is not in a legal guarding position when he steps into Anunoby's (TOR) path and initiates foot contact that affects his SQBR.
Ibaka (TOR) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Ibaka (TOR) sets the pick in Bridges's (CHA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Bridges (CHA) places a marginal hand to Ibaka's (TOR) body during his shooting motion.
Graham (CHA) moves laterally into Lowry's (TOR) path during the drive and affects his SQBR.
Zeller (CHA) sets the pick in McCaw's (TOR) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Rozier (CHA) makes contact with Ibaka's (TOR) arm during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Lowry (TOR) commits a take foul on Rozier (CHA).
During the screen, Davis (TOR) and Rozier (CHA) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Davis (TOR) legally contests Rozier's (CHA) jump shot attempt.
